img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ee9ffef9ecb303e104c48ca68a284dc07a316e","tid":122351,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機械 電機 唔係又話煲已爆咩"},{"pid":"628ea3bfaf664b72a61cea59654afb93dc04d38b","tid":122351,"uid":58683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你想多啲時間做自己野 hku囉<br />\nlab多數一科做一次 佔10-15%<br />\nMidterm 佔10-15%<br />\n其餘exam<br />\n所以個grade係exam決定<br />\n如果你唔上堂 每科每年返去三次左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上你asso有底 啲野你會易上手過jupas嘅同學好多<br />\n過3唔難<br />\n<br />\n睇你想點過 要個學校名 定要真材實料</blockquote><br />\n真材實料for sure<br />\n出黎做野無料搵鬼到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做啲野做死人就唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhku engine個學習模式好聽d就自由 可以揀合適自己嘅學習方法 所以好少take attendance exam定生死<br />\n難聽d就由你自生自滅<br />\nprof tutor 好hea理得你死<br />\n你唔識唔關佢事<br />\n當然問prof點都會答下你<br />\n我就遇過tutor email都唔覆<br />\n資源又少 連tutorial都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想學野就ust啦<br />\nchur就chur d<br />\n但點都容易學好d<br />\n<br />\n如果你鍾意hku個名就hku<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申hku civil</span></span>"},{"pid":"698b2be72d96dc5f1cca9891cb806819b15e8f18","tid":122351,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9先入hku mech  <br />\n利申on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解</blockquote><br />\n太hea 老老柒柒學唔到野 lab同training渣留灘 lecture太多theory<br />\n申利：讀緊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係 lecture係hea到返唔返都冇影響<br />\n反正自己刨notes"},{"pid":"470be660fd601c8e4ae0793e2d56b3c0bdb3c3be","tid":122351,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你想多啲時間做自己野 hku囉<br />\nlab多數一科做一次 佔10-15%<br />\nMidterm 佔10-15%<br />\n其餘exam<br />\n所以個grade係exam決定<br />\n如果你唔上堂 每科每年返去三次左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上你asso有底 啲野你會易上手過jupas嘅同學好多<br />\n過3唔難<br />\n<br />\n睇你想點過 要個學校名 定要真材實料</blockquote><br />\n真材實料for sure<br />\n出黎做野無料搵鬼到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做啲野做死人就唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhku engine個學習模式好聽d就自由 可以揀合適自己嘅學習方法 所以好少take attendance exam定生死<br />\n難聽d就由你自生自滅<br />\nprof tutor 好hea理得你死<br />\n你唔識唔關佢事<br />\n當然問prof點都會答下你<br />\n我就遇過tutor email都唔覆<br />\n資源又少 連tutorial都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想學野就ust啦<br />\nchur就chur d<br />\n但點都容易學好d<br />\n<br />\n如果你鍾意hku個名就hku<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申hku civil</span></span></blockquote><br />\nmech好多科一個sem得2堂tut<br />\n有啲prof直情唔想人搵佢問野 覺得阻住佢做研究咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e19dfe36105cf7832a29d87561e4434c235c097","tid":122351,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主收得yr3 hku offer gpa應該最少都3.6以上 你仲有更多好嘅選擇 好好諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擇咩阿 我FORM都交晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be92357b89a2fa3d033b7471637c6b272a75737d","tid":122351,"uid":58683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你想多啲時間做自己野 hku囉<br />\nlab多數一科做一次 佔10-15%<br />\nMidterm 佔10-15%<br />\n其餘exam<br />\n所以個grade係exam決定<br />\n如果你唔上堂 每科每年返去三次左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上你asso有底 啲野你會易上手過jupas嘅同學好多<br />\n過3唔難<br />\n<br />\n睇你想點過 要個學校名 定要真材實料</blockquote><br />\n真材實料for sure<br />\n出黎做野無料搵鬼到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做啲野做死人就唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhku engine個學習模式好聽d就自由 可以揀合適自己嘅學習方法 所以好少take attendance exam定生死<br />\n難聽d就由你自生自滅<br />\nprof tutor 好hea理得你死<br />\n你唔識唔關佢事<br />\n當然問prof點都會答下你<br />\n我就遇過tutor email都唔覆<br />\n資源又少 連tutorial都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想學野就ust啦<br />\nchur就chur d<br />\n但點都容易學好d<br />\n<br />\n如果你鍾意hku個名就hku<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申hku civil</span></span></blockquote><br />\nmech好多科一個sem得2堂tut<br />\n有啲prof直情唔想人搵佢問野 覺得阻住佢做研究咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下你夠唔夠厚面皮<br />\n上堂前後當住面問佢點都答嘅<br />\n佢都唔好意思唔理你<br />\n最多黑你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba2cfb5d88e286c873b79efa161d63049c8f633","tid":122351,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有HKU offer都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2444361290108fc06f18ec90998043c9d5c54b5b","tid":122351,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有HKU offer都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKU Engine好似好雞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺讀engine要係POLYU or UST讀<br />\n<br />\n姐係讀醫要係HKU or CU讀同理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c3418b284bd57fd620a56589a5803ac24a23e6","tid":122351,"uid":73715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:54:19.000Z",